{"allowModDistribution":true,"screenshots":[{"description":"A mischievous low-rank demon, quick and elusive, capable of cloning itself upon death.","id":1009986,"title":"Imp","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1009/986/imp.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1009/986/310/172/imp.png"},{"description":"A cursed suit of armor that comes to life, attacking those who venture too close.","id":1009987,"title":"Possessed Armor","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1009/987/possessed_armor.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1009/987/310/172/possessed_armor.png"},{"description":"A stoic and fearsome stone sentinel, dormant by day and vigilant by night, fiercely protecting its domain from intruders.","id":1024052,"title":"Gargoyle","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1024/52/gargoyle.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1024/52/310/172/gargoyle.png"},{"description":"A mysterious and imposing spectral cowboy, clad in dark, tattered attire. By night, he roams the land, collecting lost souls and delivering judgment to those who cross his path.","id":1058886,"title":"The Black Charro","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1058/886/black_charro.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1058/886/310/172/black_charro.png"},{"description":"A tormented spirit wandering the Soul Sand Valleys, driven by anguish and rage. Cloaked in mist and sorrow, it attacks the living in a desperate bid for freedom. Summoned by the Black Charro or found naturally, it serves as a harbinger of doom.","id":1196159,"title":"Condemned Soul","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1196/159/image_2025-05-21_143742458-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1196/159/310/172/image_2025-05-21_143742458-png.png"},{"description":"A sly, passive creature that snatches items from unsuspecting travelers before vanishing into the shadows, leaving only mischief behind.","id":1348258,"title":"Alp","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1348/258/alp-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1348/258/310/172/alp-png.png"},{"description":"The ultimate enforcer of its cursed faction, the Inquisitor wields dark powers and deadly precision, leaving no intruder unchallenged.","id":1348263,"title":"Possessed Armor Inquisitor","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1348/263/possessed_armor_inquisitor-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1348/263/310/172/possessed_armor_inquisitor-png.png"},{"description":"A towering infernal creature that commands fiery spikes from the ground, Abaddon punishes intruders with relentless fire and brute strength.","id":1348266,"title":"Abaddon","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1348/266/abaddon-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1348/266/310/172/abaddon-png.png"},{"description":"A savage beast of the snow, Karakondjul hunts with primal ferocity, blending into frozen landscapes to ambush its prey.","id":1348267,"title":"Karakondjul","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1348/267/karakondjul-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1348/267/310/172/karakondjul-png.png"},{"description":"A black humanoid guardian of the Scorched Nests, its twin horns and golden armlets mark its authority, while its whip-like tail strikes those who threaten its domain.","id":1348261,"title":"Scorched Sentinel","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1348/261/scorched_sentinel-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1348/261/310/172/scorched_sentinel-png.png"},{"description":"A mysterious humanoid of the Nether forests, Lampad carries a lantern with a flickering green flame, appearing suddenly to unsettle wanderers.","id":1348268,"title":"Lampad","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1348/268/lampad-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1348/268/310/172/lampad-png.png"},{"description":"A legendary beast of the frozen wilds, the Amarok hunts alone beneath the full moon, striking with relentless strength and supernatural ferocity.","id":1408443,"title":"Amarok","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1408/443/amarok-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1408/443/310/172/amarok-png.png"},{"description":"possessed-armor-in-game.png","id":1214983,"title":"possessed-armor-in-game.png","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1214/983/possessed-armor-in-game-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1214/983/310/172/possessed-armor-in-game-png.png"},{"description":"gargoyle-in-game.png","id":1214981,"title":"gargoyle-in-game.png","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1214/981/gargoyle-in-game-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1214/981/310/172/gargoyle-in-game-png.png"},{"description":"imp-in-game.png","id":1214982,"title":"imp-in-game.png","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1214/982/imp-in-game-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1214/982/310/172/imp-in-game-png.png"},{"description":"condemned-soul-in-game.png","id":1214980,"title":"condemned-soul-in-game.png","modId":1133244,"url":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1214/980/condemned-soul-in-game-png.png","thumbnailUrl":"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/thumbnails/1214/980/310/172/condemned-soul-in-game-png.png"},{"description":"black-charro-in-game.png","id":1214984,"title":"black-charro-in-game.png","modI